SIMPLE: blinkard
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Blinkard
<hw>Blink"ard</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Blind</ets>
+ <ets>-ard</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who blinks with, or as
with, weak eyes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Among the blind the one-eyed <qex>blinkard</qex> reigns.</q>
<rj><qau>Marvell.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which twinkles or glances, as a dim star, which
appears and disappears.</def> <rj><au>Hakewill.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blink beer</ent>⟦br⟧
